data.description: New Price! Beautiful remodel home in walking distance to Corner Lake Middle School and shopping. Roof was installed in 2021, brand new paint inside and out of the house. New landscaping and the garage has been painted including the garage floor. Remodeled new kitchen with brand new appliances, tiled back splash, new white wood shaker cabinets and new granite. Brand new ceiling fans, blinds and lighting throughout the house. Master bedroom has new tile complimenting the new tiled master shower. Beautiful custom mirror, and lighting with a new shower head too. The second bath has a new vanity, paint and lighting. The house has new vinyl wood flooring in two bedrooms and the rest of the home including the enclosed back porch area. This home has access to the following amenities, including a playground, picnic area, and a basketball court. The community is conveniently located near UCF, Full Sail University, and downtown, easy access to 408,417,528.
